OL,6,FITV News' Business and Economics
OL,7,FEditor, Joel Hills has the latest on
OL,8,Fwhat it could mean for our finances.
OL,10,FMarkets around the world have seen
OL,11,Fstocks plunge downwards, including
OL,12,FFTSE 100 and Japan's Nikkei 225 index,
OL,13,Fwhich suffered its worst day since
OL,14,F1987.
