OL,3,CWall Street tumbles as global stock
OL,4,Cmarket sell-off takes hold
OL,6,FNasdaq composite slid 5.5% to pull it
OL,7,F15% below its record set last month.
OL,9,FMarkets in Asia, suffered similar
OL,10,Fdownward turns, with Japan's Nikkei
OL,11,F225 plunged 12.4% for its worst day
OL,12,Fsince the Black Monday crash of 1987.
OL,14,FThe Japanese benchmark index fell
OL,15,F4,451 points to 31,458 on Monday.
OL,17,FThe global stock market sell-off was
OL,18,Fsparked by a jobs report released on
OL,19,FFriday, showing US employers slowed
OL,20,Fhiring last month by much more than
OL,21,Feconomists expected.
