OL,4,Cmarket sell-off takes hold
OL,6,FIt comes as the latest in a series of
OL,7,Fdata releases on the US economy, which
OL,8,Fhave all come in weaker than expected,
OL,9,Fwhich has left investors spooked at
OL,10,Fthe prospect of a potential American
OL,11,Frecession.
