OL,3,CWall Street tumbles as global stock
OL,4,Cmarket sell-off takes hold
OL,6,FThis has prompted fears the country's
OL,7,FFederal Reserve has put the brakes on
OL,8,Fthe US economy by too much for too
OL,9,Flong through high interest rates in
OL,10,Fhopes of stifling inflation.
OL,12,FLosses elsewhere in the world were
OL,13,Fsignificant, with South Korea's Kospi
OL,14,Findex went 8.8% lower, and bitcoin
OL,15,Fdropped 12%.
OL,17,FEven gold, which has a reputation for
OL,18,Foffering safety during tumultuous
OL,19,Ftimes, slipped nearly 2%.
